#
# Policy: icmp-safe
# Description:
#  Allow safe types of ICMP/ICMPv6 packets

policy in ip protocol icmp icmp type {echo-reply, destination-unreachable, echo-request, time-exceeded} accept
policy in ip6 nexthdr icmpv6 icmpv6 type {echo-reply, destination-unreachable, echo-request, time-exceeded,packet-too-big, nd-neighbor-solicit, nd-neighbor-advert} accept
